      "content": "that's a great start. i want to make the counter-arguments look even weaker. like, when people bring up 'meritocracy' or say it's 'unfair' to take from people who worked hard, how can i frame those views in the essay so it's clear they're just excuses to maintain a biased system? i want to show that their logic is actually just a way to ignore the historical facts you mentioned.",
